{"tid":1473770,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"戴耀廷准保釋　明年2月上訴聆訊","createTime":"2019-08-15T02:57:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-15T03:03:09.000Z","uid":285899,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"dfe608d4c05df638e72b4ff6175af26dee147f68","tid":1473770,"uid":285899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T02:57:02.000Z","msg":"因「佔中九子」案被判囚16個月的戴耀廷，目前在大嶼山石壁監獄服刑。他早前就定罪和判刑提出上訴，今（15日）在高等法院申請保釋等候上訴。上訴庭副庭長麥機智聽畢陳辭後批准戴耀廷的保釋。上訴聆訊將於明年2月24至26日進行。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20190815/s00001/1565837343560\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20190815%2Fs00001%2F1565837343560&d=uCt0JTl3CznPmZ5dgdQeg5B82cw%2Bhl0zMn8EQHxvzrU%3D&h=db88db26\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20190815%2Fs00001%2F1565837343560&h=0e8d9a32\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20190815/s00001/1565837343560</a>"},{"pid":"2142dd9cdd7265c49696938ba6655f9fa85e9a85","tid":1473770,"uid":264724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T02:57:59.000Z","msg":"求推求推! 超簡單 全民集氣方法 一定要谷到 全香港支持運動嘅人都識做<br />\n<br />\n全民係屋企都可以示威:<br />\nN<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">oise-Making&nbsp;定時敲鑊抗爭法</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1469010\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1469010</a>"},{"pid":"25fd2a06afdc503d89f0a930448a4ef71f22169a","tid":1473770,"uid":60615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T03:02:36.000Z","msg":"18號俾狗扑濕再告煽惑暴動<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81368ebdb1514877568268e01dcdc4d7b89f82bf","tid":1473770,"uid":171992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T03:03:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/6yR8ycR.jpg\" data-th